  <metadata>
    <id>Microsoft.Storage.Pickers</id>
    <version>1.0.0</version>
    <authors>Mahdi Hosseini</authors>
    <description>
		This NuGet package provides access to the Microsoft.Storage.Picker API from the Microsoft WindowsAppSdk. 
		The API is currently in prototype stage and allows you to integrate a powerful and customizable file picker into your Windows applications.
		It supports features like elevated apps, selecting multiple files, setting default file names, specifying file extensions, and defining default locations for file selection.
	</description>
